ssroads Cebu’s focus is to contribute to creative economy’s growth in the city by showcasing some of the best local brands alongside art, design, and craft showroom-gallery spaces in a work-play community.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"_4bl9\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"_4bl7\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"_5aj7 _3-8j\"></div>\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:12:\"A-Space Cebu\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:4:\"open\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:28:\"crossroads-cebu-a-space-cebu\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2019-07-21 13:19:03\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2019-07-21 13:19:03\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:70:\"http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=229\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:-1;s:9:\"post_type\";s:11:\"job_listing\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:205;s:11:\"post_author\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2017-07-25 13:18:47\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2017-07-25 13:18:47\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:1449:\"STARTINNO IS BYRON BAY\'S MOST VIBRANT AND PRODUCTIVE HUB FOR CREATIVES, INNOVATORS AND ENTREPRENEURS TO WORK.\r\n\r\nWE\'RE NOT JUST A COWORKING AND SHARED OFFICE SPACE, BUT A COMMUNITY.\r\nWE ARE A TRUE HUB OF PEOPLE LIVING AND BUILDING THEIR DREAMS.\r\n\r\nThe coworking hub is a shared space for creative entrepreneurs. Whether you are a digital nomad, cubical escapee to just want to get out of the home office into a vibrant, postitive and collaborative environment, the hub is the place for you.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nReady to jump off the waterfall and create your own business? Innovation is a great place to #juststart. Whether you need help with a new idea, or an existing business or corporate that wants to grow, find out more about out our lean startup programs\r\n<h2>Co-Working Space</h2>\r\nThe shared office and coworking hub includes FAST 30/10Mps high-speed wireless internet (WDSL3 &amp; ADSL as backup), choice of seating &amp; stand-up desks, private Skype-booths, access to fast wifi printing &amp; scanning, meeting areas, all set in a modern creative space. More importantly, the StartInno gives you access to a true Hub that is dynamic, exciting and a collaborative space where you can meet other people living and building their dreams. We also have the <strong>best coffee </strong>and<strong> locally sourced food</strong> with <a href=\"http://100miletable.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">100 Mile Table</a> right next door!\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:47:\"StartInno Coworking and Innovation Hub in Byron\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"expired\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:4:\"open\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:3:\"205\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2017-08-25 10:36:43\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2017-08-25 10:36:43\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:70:\"http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=205\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:-1;s:9:\"post_type\";s:11:\"job_listing\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:2;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:185;s:11:\"post_author\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2017-07-25 12:45:07\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2017-07-25 12:45:07\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:347:\"<h1>One Space leads the way in events to move you. One Space HQ Bondi is our new community venue.</h1>\r\n<a href=\"http://onespace.com.au/one-space-hq/\"><strong>One Space HQ</strong></a> was opened June 2016, and aims to bring the Sydney community a unique space to host, workshop, intimate concerts, classes to uplift and inspire us to live as one.\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:9:\"One Space\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"expired\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:4:\"open\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:9:\"one-space\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2017-08-25 10:36:43\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2017-08-25 10:36:43\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:70:\"http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=185\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:-1;s:9:\"post_type\";s:11:\"job_listing\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:3;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:273;s:11:\"post_author\";s:1:\"6\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2019-07-21 13:18:22\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2019-07-21 13:18:22\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:1689:\"We are looking for a new flatmate for our beach site apartment in Maroubra.\r\n??‍♀️??‍♂️?????\r\n\r\nWe are in a great spot on Severn St, (arguably one the best streets in Maroubra)\r\n\r\nThe room is bright and cozy with ocean views, queen bed and large wardrobe.\r\n\r\nThe apartment is specious with large balcony overlooking the beach. Two bathrooms and 3 bedrooms. The building has a backyard with bbq and veggie garden\r\n\r\nMaroubra is one of the best surfing beaches in Sydney and it has a great community feel.\r\n\r\nThere is a surf school, national park with hiking tracks, Pilates studio, yoga studio, gym, indoor and outdoor pool. Plenty of places to grab a coffee, beer or something to eat. Only half hour to the city by bus, plenty of parking on the street and only 10 minutes to Coogee or Randwick.\r\n\r\nAtm moment there is 3 of us, one couple ( CZ and AU ) and one guy ( CZ ) who will be moving out within next 3 months and we wont be replacing him with anyone else.\r\n\r\nWe are all active and like to eat healthy. Always keen to do things: go to gigs, hiking, surf trips, road trips, art shows and other fun things that Sydney has to offer.\r\n\r\nWe are in our 30\'s and although we are growing up and being responsible, we still like to enjoy ourselves and will occasionally hold a BBQ in the backyard and have friends over. Or we like to pop in to the the local pub that has great food and it is a great place to have a drink if the day has been long.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for someone in similar mind set. Someone clean and tidy with full time job preferably.\r\n\r\nThe length of stay is negotiable starting at 2 months, so let us know what you\'re looking for.\r\n\r\n$300 per week\r\n\r\nNo couples\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:18:\"Creative Beach Pad\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:4:\"open\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:34:\"maroubra-sydney-creative-beach-pad\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2019-07-21 13:19:04\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2019-07-21 13:19:04\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:80:\"http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/listing/maroubra-sydney-creative-beach-pad/\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"post_type\";s:11:\"job_listing\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:4;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:249;s:11:\"post_author\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2017-07-25 14:01:21\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2017-07-25 14:01:21\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:4:\"FRAT\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:4:\"open\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:4:\"frat\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"pos