mt\";s:19:\"2017-08-25 10:36:43\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:70:\"http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=189\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"post_type\";s:11:\"job_listing\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:10;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:172;s:11:\"post_author\";s:1:\"2\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2017-07-03 05:19:59\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2017-07-03 05:19:59\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:2657:\"<h1>Live in Work Space</h1>\r\n<h4><strong>Availability: 31st Oct - 13th Nov (2 weeks)</strong></h4>\r\nWe are looking for short term flatmate for our awesome beach pad in Maroubra (3rd Nov – 27 Nov).\r\n\r\nThe room is bright and cosy with ocean views, queen bed and large wardrobe. The apartment is specious with large balcony overlooking the beach.\r\n\r\nMaroubra is one of the best surfing beaches in Sydney and it has a great community feel, there is a surf school, national park with hiking tracks, Pilates studio, yoga stud<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">io, gym, indoor and outdoor pool. Plenty of places to grab a coffee, beer or something to eat. Only half hour to the city by bus, plenty of parking on the street and only 10 minutes to Coogee or Randwick. </span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">\r\nWe are social, outdoorsy and pretty chilled bunch, not party animals, but like to site back on the balcony overlooking the beach and have the occasional beer or wine.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Digital Village</h3>\r\nDigital Village is a network of digital specialists where members will have access to places all around the world to stay with other creatives and tech-heads. This site is for the Digital Nomad. If your working and travelling, come and stay here for a while.\r\n\r\nStay up to date with technology, be part of community, meet people in your industry all around the world.  Come to stay and work from an office and creative space in our beautiful apartment overlooking the forever picturesque Maroubra Beach.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Why?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Your own room with ocean views and space to work.</li>\r\n 	<li>Communal office space</li>\r\n 	<li>surfboard use</li>\r\n 	<li>fast internet</li>\r\n 	<li>work in collaborative environment</li>\r\n 	<li>Join in on Jam sessions around startups and business ideas</li>\r\n 	<li>build products</li>\r\n 	<li>Network</li>\r\n 	<li>Guides around Sydney creative scene</li>\r\n 	<li>get a tattoo (if you want)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>The Apartment/Office Space</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>20 metres from awesome cafes and bars</li>\r\n 	<li>20 metres to beach</li>\r\n 	<li>20 metres to yoga studios</li>\r\n 	<li>30 minute bus to CBD</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Your Village Mates</h2>\r\n<strong>Andrea</strong>\r\n\r\nA Fine Artist that works from her home studio. A lover of music, wine, the arts and a good time. A travelling tattoo artist with a passion for design and creating new things.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Jason</strong>\r\n\r\nFounder of Digital Village. Easy going and enjoys brainstorming new ideas and talking tech and innovation. Live an active and healthy lifestyle while still enjoying the good times. You can\'t take life too seriously....\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:27:\"Maroubra Beach Creative Pad\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:4:\"open\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:42:\"maroubra-beach-maroubra-beach-creative-pad\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2018-10-11 09:52:42\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2018-10-11 09:52:42\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:88:\"http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/listing/maroubra-beach-maroubra-beach-creative-pad/\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"post_type\";s:11:\"job_listin