7:\"expired\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:4:\"open\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:9:\"one-space\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2017-08-25 10:36:43\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2017-08-25 10:36:43\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:70:\"http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=185\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:-1;s:9:\"post_type\";s:11:\"job_listing\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:273;s:11:\"post_author\";s:1:\"6\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2019-07-21 13:18:22\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2019-07-21 13:18:22\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:1689:\"We are looking for a new flatmate for our beach site apartment in Maroubra.\r\n??‍♀️??‍♂️?????\r\n\r\nWe are in a great spot on Severn St, (arguably one the best streets in Maroubra)\r\n\r\nThe room is bright and cozy with ocean views, queen bed and large wardrobe.\r\n\r\nThe apartment is specious with large balcony overlooking the beach. Two bathrooms and 3 bedrooms. The building has a backyard with bbq and veggie garden\r\n\r\nMaroubra is one of the best surfing beaches in Sydney and it has a great community feel.\r\n\r\nThere is a surf school, national park with hiking tracks, Pilates studio, yoga studio, gym, indoor and outdoor pool. Plenty of places to grab a coffee, beer or something to eat. Only half hour to the city by bus, plenty of parking on the street and only 10 minutes to Coogee or Randwick.\r\n\r\nAtm moment there is 3 of us, one couple ( CZ and AU ) and one guy ( CZ ) who will be moving out within next 3 months and we wont be replacing him with anyone else.\r\n\r\nWe are all active and like to eat healthy. Always keen to do things: go to gigs, hiking, surf trips, road trips, art shows and other fun things that Sydney has to offer.\r\n\r\nWe are in our 30\'s and although we are growing up and being responsible, we still like to enjoy ourselves and will occasionally hold a BBQ in the backyard and have friends over. Or we like to pop in to the the local pub that has great food and it is a great place to have a drink if the day has been long.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for someone in similar mind set. Someone clean and tidy with full time job preferably.\r\n\r\nThe length of stay is negotiable starting at 2 months, so let us know what you\'re looking for.\r\n\r\n$300 per week\r\n\r\nNo couples\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:18:\"Creative Beach Pad\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:4:\"open\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:34:\"maroubra-sydney-creative-beach-pad\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2019-07-21 13:19:04\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2019-07-21 13:19:04\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:80:\"http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/listing/maroubra-sydney-creative-beach-pad/\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"post_type\";s:11:\"job_listing\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:2;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:220;s:11:\"post_author\";s:1:\"2\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2017-07-25 13:32:30\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2017-07-25 13:32:30\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:204:\"A place where friends and families come to meet after a swim, surf and play.\r\nFresh honest food is our philosophy. All our food including cakes, jams and muffins are home made, and we use Salvador Coffee.\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:18:\"The North End Cafe\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"expired\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:4:\"open\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:18:\"the-north-end-caf