ets change that, lets shake this body like at an awkward school dance. </i></b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><i>In South East Asia, the heart rate pumps fast.</i></b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><i>Few rules, little restriction, excitement depicts them.</i></b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><i>With a high blood cell count, the city is thriving.</i></b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><i>Eager to help, mischevious and conniving. </i></b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><i>Greece and Rome once powerhouses and the Alpha dogs, now sit stale and geriatric like a beautiful, wise old man that has seen a thing or two. </i></b>','The Family Gathering','','draft','open','open','','','','','2017-06-12 02:47:03','2017-06-12 02:47:03','',0,'http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/?p=161',0,'post','',0),(162,1,'2017-06-12 02:47:03','2017-06-12 02:47:03','<b><i>Earth\'s a big place, but it’s just a small family.</i></b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><i>With Elders and youngsters, the buried and unborn. </i></b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><i>The annual family reunion, </i></b>\r\n\r\n<b><i>An event not be missed and impossible to avoid</i></b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><i>Greece &amp; Rome still expecting a sweet, easy retirement, look to a frustrated Germany who begrudgingly pays their pension and gets back to their business.</i></b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><i>The annoying cousin from the US storms in causing trouble and spreading rumours.</i></b>\r\n\r\n<b><i>Adding fuel to the fire where tempers flare and oil wells boil over.</i></b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><i>A frale England sits in the corner by themselves, murmuring and shifting as a weathered face of France is on the opposite side giving England the finger with a cigarette in the side of their mouth. </i></b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><i>Ireland and Scotland have been drunk since 8am </i></b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><i>Russia is drunk and telling 