 can get lonely and uninspiring. Why not rent your room out as an office/live in office?\r\n<h3 class=\"ion-person-add\">1. Create an Account</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-full\" src=\"http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/page-how-it-works-1.png\" width=\"180px\" />Creating an account with Digital Village Nomads is easy. Fill out the<a href=\"http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/myaccount/\"> basic form</a> for information about yourself and your good to go.\r\n<h3 class=\"ion-compose\">2. Submit Your Listing</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full\" src=\"http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/page-how-it-works-3.png\" width=\"220px\" />\r\nSubmitting a listing is super simple, we’ve made entering the address of your place easy, by implementing the Google Places API to auto complete the listing address. (Thankyou Uncle Google)\r\n<h3 class=\"ion-bag\">3. Get More Interest In Your Place</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-full\" width=\"220px\" />\r\n\r\nThis is a simple but exciting idea to allow Digital Nomads to continue their world adventures and remain in contact with their industry and people in the industry by staying with people that also work in the tech industry.\r\n\r\nWho knows, you may even start working together!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button\" href=\"http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/add-your-listing/\">Get Started Now</a></p>','How it Works','','inherit','closed','closed','','40-revision-v1','','','2017-06-12 02:54:58','2017-06-12 02:54:58','',40,'http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/2017/06/12/40-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(168,1,'2017-07-01 06:52:10','2017-07-01 06:52:10','','kiev','','inherit','open','closed','','kiev','','','2017-07-01 06:52:20','2017-07-01 06:52:20','',0,'http://nomads.digitalvillage.network/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/kiev.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(169,1,'2017-07-01 06:54:45','2017-07-01 06:54:45','','lahore',''